### 1. 회원가입
POST localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test1234",
    "password": "1234",
    "email": "test1234@test.com",
    "slackId": "test1234",
    "role" : "ROLE_COMPANY"
}





### 2. 로그인
